hadiths[72]{hadithnumber,text}:
6952,"Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya : mere barey mein mere bandey ka jo guman ho mein iske sath (mutabiq hota) hun aur wo mujhey jahan ( bhi) yad karey mein uske paas hota hun. Allah ki qism ! Allah Taala apne bandey ki tauba par tum mein se aisey aadmi ki nisbat bhi zyada khush hota hai jisey chatiyal biyaabaan main apni gum shuda sawari (saman samet wapas ( mil jati hai. ( mera ( jo banda aik baalisht mere qareeb aata hai, main aik hath iske qareeb aa jata hun aur jo aik hath mere qareeb hota hai, main donon hathon ki poori lambai ke barabar iske qareeb ho jata hun aur jo chalta hua meri taraf aata hai, main daudta hua uske paas aata hun."
6953,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala yaqinan tum mein se kisi ke tauba karne par us se zyada khush hota hai jitna tum mein se koi shakhs apni gum shuda sawari ( wapas ( pa kar khush hota hai."
6954,Hammam-bin-Munabba ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ke ham mana riwayat ki.
6955,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Umara bin Umer se aur unhon-ne Haris bin Suwed se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ke yahan hazir hua, us waqt wo bimar they, unhon-ne hamein 2 hadisein bayan kin, aik hadis apni taraf se aur aik hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : Allah Taala apne momin bandey ki tauba par us se zyada khush hota hai jitna wo aadmi ( khush hota hai) jo halaak kar dene wale sunsaan aur be aab w giyaah maidan mein ho, iske sath uski sawari ho, us ( sawari ( par uska khana aur pani lada hua ho, wo (thaka-haara kuchh der ke liye) so jaey aur jab jaagey to sawari ja chuki ho. wo dhoondta rahe yahan tak ke usey shadeed piyaas lag jaey, phir wo kahey : main jahan par tha, usi jagah wapas jata hun aur so jata hun, yahan tak ke (is neend ke aalim mein) mujhey maut aa jaey. wo apni kalaai par sar rakh kar marney ke liye let jaey aur) achcha ( uski aankh khuley to uski wo sawari jis par uska zaade-raah khana aur pani tha uske paas khadi ho. to Allah apne momin bandey ki tauba par us se zyada khush hota hai jitna ye aadmi apni sawari aur zaade-raah se khush hota hai."
6956,"Qutba bin Abdul-Azeez ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur kaha is aadmi ki nisbat ( zyada khush hota hai) jo zamin ke sunsaan be aab w giyaah sehra mein ho. ( دويۃ (ke bajaey ( daawiya (ka lafz bola, ( mana aik hi hai.)"
6957,"abu-Usama ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Umara bin Umer ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Haris bin Suwed se suna, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne 2 hadisein bayan kin, aik Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( naql kartey huey) aur dusri apni taraf se, chunanche unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah Allah apne momin bandey ki tauba se (us aadmi ki nisbat) zyada khush hota hai) aagey ( Jarir ki hadis ki tarah."
6958,"abu Yunus ne Samak se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ne khutba diya aur (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka farman ( bayan kya : Allah Taala ko apne bandey ki tauba par us shakhs ki nisbat zyada khushi hoti hai jisne apna zaade-raah aur apni pani ki badi mashk ko oont par laada, phir (safar par) chal pada, yahan tak ke jab wo aik chatiyal zamin par tha to usey do-pahar ki neend ne be bas kar diya, wo utra aur aik darakht ke nichey do-pahar ke aaraam ke liye let gaya, uski aankh lag gaee aur iska oont kisi taraf ko nikal gaya, phir wo jaaga to koshish karke aik teeley par chadha (har taraf dekha) lekin usey kuchh nazar na aaya, phir wo mashaqqat utha kar doosrey teeley par chadha, usey kuchh nazar na aaya, phir ( mazeed ( mashaqqat se teesrey teeley par chadha to usey kuchh nazar na aaya, phir wo aaya, usi jagah pahuncha jahan do-pahar ka aaraam kya tha, wo (is jagah ( betha hua tha ke uska oont chalta hua ( wapas ( aa gaya aur apni mahaar ( nakel se bandhi hui rassi) us aadmi ke hath par gira di. ( usey uth kar mahaar pakadney ki zahmat bhi na karni padi ( to Allah apne bandey ki tauba par us shakhs ki nisbat zyada khush hota hai jab ye aadmi apni sawari ko uski asl haalat main ( zaade-raah aur pani samet sahi Salim ( pa leta hai. Samak ne kaha : to Shabi ne samjha ke Hazrat Nauman (bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu)) ne ye baat marfoo (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se) bayan ki hai, lekin maine unko ( marfoo bayan kartey ( nahi suna."
6959,"Yahya-bin-Yahya aur Jafar bin Humaid ne hamein Ubaidullah bin Iyaad bin Laqeet se, unhon-ne yad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum us shakhs ki khushi ke mutaalliq kya kehtey ho jiski ontni aisi be aab w giyaah zamin mein, jahan khaney ki koi cheez ho na peeney ki, apni nakel ki rassi kheenchti hui (kisi taraf) nikal gaee. uska khana aur pani bhi usi par tha. us shakhs ne usey (bahut) dhoonda yahan tak ke thak kar haar gaya, phir wo ( ontni chaltey-chaltey) aik darakht ke mazbut taney ke paas se guzri to uski nakel ki rassi iske sath atak gaee aur us shakhs ne us (ontni) ko us (taney) ke sath lagi khadi pa liya? ham ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! (is shakhs ki khushi) be-panah hogi. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala apne bandey ki tauba par us se kahin zyada khush hota hai jitna ye shakhs apni sawari ko pa kar hota hai. Jafar ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah bin Iyaad ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki."
6960,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki aur wo (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) unke chacha hain, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala apne bandey ki tauba par, jab wo ( banda) uski taraf tauba karta hai, tum mein se kisi aisey shakhs ki nisbat kahin zyada khush hota hai jo aik be-aab w giyaah sehraa main apni sawari par (safar kar raha) tha to wo uske hath se nikal (kar gum ho ( gaee, uska khana aur pani usi (sawari) par hai. wo us (ke milney ( se maayoos ho gaya to aik darakht ke paas aaya aur uske saaey mein let gaya. wo apni sawari (milney) se naa-ummeed ho chuka tha. wo usi aalim mein hai ke achcha wo (aadmi) uske paas hai, wo (ontni) uske paas khadi hai, us ne usko nakel ki rassi se pakad liya, phir be panah khushi ki shiddat mein keh betha, aey Allah! to mera banda hai aur main tera rab hun. khushi ki shiddat ki wjah se ghalati kar gaya."
6961,"Haddab bin Khalid ne kaha : hamein Hammam ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ko apne bandey ki tauba se, tum mein se kisi aisey shakhs ki nisbat kahin zyada khushi hoti hai jab chatiyal sehraa mein uske (us ( oont (ke aaney) par uski aankh khulti hai jisey wo sehra mein gum kar chuka hota hai."
6962,"Hibban ne kaha : hamein Hammam ne hadis bayan ki. kaha : hamein Qatada ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
6963,"Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez ke qissa bhale hi Muhammad-bin-Qais ne abu-Sarma se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke jab unki wafat ka waqt aaya to unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hui aik hadis tum se chipa rakhi thi, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna tha : agar tum (log) gunah na karo to (tumhari jagah ( Allah Taala aisi makhlooq ko paida farma de jo gunah karein (phir Allah se tauba karein aur) wo unki maghfirat farma de."
6964,"Muhammad-bin Kab Qarzi ne abu-Sarma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tum aisey hotey ke tumharey ( naamaae-aamaal mein kuchh bhi) gunah na hotey jinki Allah Taala tumharey liye bakhshish farmata to wo aisi qaum ko (is duniya mein) ley aata jinke gunah hotey aur wo unke liye un (gunahon) ki maghfirat farmata."
6965,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! agar tum (log) gunah na karo to Allah Taala tum ko (is duniya se) ley jaey aur) tumharey badley mein) aisi qaum ko ley aaey jo gunah karein aur Allah Taala se maghfirat maangein to wo unki maghfirat farmaai ."
6966,"Jafar bin Sulaiman ne Saeed bin Ayas Jurairi se, unhon-ne abu-Usman nehdi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Hanzala (bin Rabe ( Usaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha, padhi. aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kaatibon mein se they. kaha : Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) mujh se miley aur malum kya : Hanzala ! aap kaisey hain? maine kaha : Hanzala munafiq ho gaya hai, (Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Subhan-Allah ! tum kya keh rahe ho? maine kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hotey hain, aap hamein jannat aur dozakh ki yad dilaatey hain yahan tak ke aisey lagtey hain maano ham (unhein ( aankhon se dekh rahe hain, phir jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan se nikaltey hain to beeviyon , bachchon aur kheti baadi (aur doosrey kaam kaaj) ko sanbhaalney mein lag jatey hain aur bahut si cheezein bhool jatey hain. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! yahi kuchh hamein bhi pesh aata hai, phir main aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) chal padey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! Hanzala munafiq ho gaya hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo kya mamla hai? maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! ham aap ke paas hazir hotey hain, aap hamein jannat aur dozakh ki yad dilaatey hain, to haalat ye hoti hai maano ham ( jannat aur dozakh ko) apni aankhon se dekh rahe hain aur jab ham aap ke yahan se bahar nikaltey hain to beeviyon , bachchon aur kaam kaaj ki dekh bhaal mein lag jatey hain. padhi. ham bahut kuchh bhool jatey hain. padhi. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen baar irshad farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! agar tum hamesha usi kaifiyat mein raho jis tarah mere paas hotey ho aur zikr mein lagey raho to tumharey bichhonon par aur tumharey raston mein Farishtey ( aa kar) tumharey sath musaafhey karein, lekin aey Hanzala ! koi ghadi kisi tarah hoti hai aur koi ghadi kisi (aur ( tarah ."
6967,"Abdus-Samad ke walid ( Abdul-Waris bin Saeed ( ne kaha : hamein Saeed Jurairi ne abu-Usman nehdi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Hanzala (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas they, to aap ne hamein waz (nasihat) farmaya aur dozakh ki yad dilai . kaha : phir main ghar aaya to bachchon ke sath hansi mazaaq kya aur biwi se khush tabai ki, phir main bahar nikla to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat hui, maine yahi baat unko batai . unhon-ne kaha : maine bhi yahi kya hai jis tarah tum ne zikr kya hai, phir ham donon Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se miley, maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! Hanzala munafiq ho gaya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye kya baat hai? to maine poori baat aap se arz kar di, phir Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jis tarah unhon-ne kya hai, maine bhi bilkul yahi kya hai) ghar ja kar biwi bachchon ke sath mashghool ho gaya. (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Hanzala (ye ( ghadi ghadi ka mamla hai (eik ghadi kisi tarah hoti hai aur dusri kisi aur tarah .) agar tumharey dil har waqt isi tarah rahen jaisey tazkeer w talqeen ke waqt hotey hain to tumharey sath Farishtey musaafhey karein yahan tak ke raston main tum ko salam kahein."
6968,"Sufiyan ne Saeed Jurairi se, unhon-ne abu-Usman nehdi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Hanzala tamimi Usaidi (Raziallahu anhu) kaatib ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hotey they aur aap hamein jannat aur dozakh ki yad dilaatey . phir un donon ( Jafar bin Sulaiman aur Abdul-Waris bin Saeed ( ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
6969,"Mughira Hizami ne abu-Zinad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne jab makhlooq ko paida farmaya to apni kitab mein likh diya aur wo ( kitab ( arsh ke uper uske paas hai : yaqinan meri rehmat mere ghazab par ghalib hogi."
6970,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne abu-Zinad se, unhon-ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya : meri rehmat mere ghazab par sabqat ley gaee hai."
6971,"Ata-bin-Mina ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne jab makhlooq ke barey mein faisla farma liya to usne apni kitab main apne uper lazim kartey huey likh diya, wo uske paas rakhi hui hai : yaqinan meri rehmat mere ghazab par ghalib rahegi."
6972,"Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : Allah Taala ne rehmat ke aik sau hissey kiye, ninyaanwe hissey apne paas rok kar rakh liye aur aik hissey zamin par utara , usi aik hissey mein se makhlooq aik doosrey par rehem karti hai yahan tak ke aik chaupaaya is dar se apna sum apne bachchey se uper utha leta hai ke kahin usko lag na jaey."
6973,"Alaa ke walid ( Abdur-Rehman ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne sau rahmatein paida kin, us ne aik rehmat apni makhlooq mein rakhi aur aik kam sau rahmatein ( aainda ke liye) apne paas chipa kar rakh lein."
6974,"Ata ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ki sau rahmatein hain, unmein se aik rehmat us ne jin aur insan, haiwaanaat aur keedon-makodon ke darmyan nazil farma di. usi (eik hissey ke zariey) se wo aik doosrey par shafqat (meharbani) kartey hain, aapas mein rehmat ka bartaw kartey hain, usi se wahshi janwar apne bachchon par shafqat kartey hain aur Allah Taala ne ninyaanwe rehmatein muakhkhar (bacha) karke rakh li hain, unse qiyamat ke din apne bandon par raham farmaeyga."
6975,"Muaz ne kaha : hamein Sulaiman Taimi ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu-Usman nehdi ne Hazrat Salman faarsi (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ki sau rehmatein hain, unmein se aik rehmat hai jiske zariey se makhlooq aapas mein aik doosrey par rehem karti hai aur ninyaanwe ( rehmatein ( qiyamat ke din ke liye ( mehfooz ( hain."
6976,Moatamir ne apne walid ( Sulaiman Taimi ( se isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki.
6977,"Daawood-bin-abi-Hind ne abu-Usmaan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : be-shak Allah Taala ne jis din aasmanon aur zamin ko paida kiya us din us ne sau rahmatein paida kin, har rahmat aasmanon aur zamin ke darmyan ki wusat ke barabar hai, us ne unmein se aik rahmat zamin mein rakhi , usi rahmat ki wjah se walida apni aulad par rahmat karti hai aur wahshi janwar aur parindey aapas mein aik doosrey ke sath rahmat ka sulook kartey hain, jab qiyamat ka din hoga to Allah Taala apni rahmaton ko us rahmat ke sath mila kar poori (sau) karega (aur bandon ke sath sau feesad rahmat ka sulook farmaeyga.)"
6978,"Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kuchh qaidi aaey, un qaidiyon mein se aik aurat kisi ko talash kar rahi thi, achcha qaidiyon mein se us aik ko bachcha mil gaya, us ne bachchey ko utha kar pet se chimtaa liya aur usko doodh pilaaney lagi. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya : kya tum samajhtey ho ke ye aurat apne bachchey ko aag mein daal degi? ham ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! agar iske bas mein ho ke usey na phainkey (to hargiz nahi phainkey gi). to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala apne bandon par is se bhi zyada raham karne wala hai jitna is aurat ko apne bachchey ke sath hai."
6979,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar momin ko ye ilm ho jaey ke Allah Taala ke paas saza kya hai to koi shakhs uski jannat ki ummeed hi na rakhey , aur agar kaafir ko ye pata chal jaey ke Allah ke paas rehmat kis qadr hai to koi aik bhi uski jannat se maayoos na ho."
6980,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aadmi jisne kabhi koi neki nahi ki thi, apne ghar walon se kaha : jab wo marey to usey jalaa dein, phir uska aadha hissey ( hawaaon mein uda kar) khushki par bikher dein aur aadha hissey samandar mein baha dein. kyonke Allah ki qism ! Allah Taala ne usey qaabu kar liya to usko zaroor-zaroor aisa azab dega jo tamam jahaanon mein se kisi ko nahi dega. chunanche jab wo aadmi mar gaya to unhon-ne wahi kiya jiska us ne hukm diya tha. Allah Taala ne khushki ko hukm diya, us shakhs ka jo bhi hissey us ( khushki ( mein tha us ne usko ikattha kar diya aur samandar ko hukm diya to jo kuchh usmein tha us ne ikattha kar diya, phir (Allah ne) us se puchha : tum ne aisa kyon kiya tha? usne kaha : mere rab ! terey dar se (aisa kiya tha) aur to sabse zyada jaanney wala hai (ke meri baat sach hai) to Allah ne (is sachchi khashiyat ki bina par) usey bakhsh diya."
6981,"Mamar ne kaha : Zohri ne mujh se kaha : kya main tumhen 2 ajeeb hadisein na sunaun? ( phir ( Zohri ne kaha : mujhey Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik shakhs ne apne aap par har qism ki zyadti ki (har gunah ka irtikaab karke khud ko mujrim banaya. ( to jab uski maut ka waqt aaya to usne apne beton ko wasiiyat ki aur kaha : jab main mar jaun to mujhey jalaa denaa, phir mujhey reza reza kar denaa, phir mujhey hawa mein, samandar mein uda dena. Allah ki qism ! agar mere rab ne mujhey qaabu kar liya to mujhey yaqinan aisa azab dega jo kisi aur ko na diya hoga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : unhon-ne uske sath yahi kya. to Allah ne zamin se kaha : jo tuney liya pura wapas kar, to wo (poorey ka pura samney) khada tha. Allah ne us se farmaya : tuney jo kya is par tumhen kis cheez ne uksaaya? usne kaha : mere parwardigar ! teri khashiyat ne. padhi. ya kaha, padhi. : terey khof ne to usi ( baat ( ki bina par us ( Allah ( ne usey bakhsh diya."
6982,"Zohri ne kaha : aur Humaid ne mujhey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aurat billi ke mamley mein jahannam mein daal di gaee jisey usne baandh rakha tha. us ne na usko khilaaya, na usey chhoda hi ke zamin ke chhotey-chhotey janwar kha leti, wo laaghar ho kar mar gaee. Zohri ne kaha : ye isliye (farmaya gaya :) hai ke koi shakhs na sirf (rehmat par) bharosa kar ley aur na sirf maayoosi hi ko apna ley."
6983,"Zubaidi ne mujhey hadis sunai ke Zohri ne kaha : mujhey humaid bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : aik bandey ne apne aap par har tarah ki zyadti ki. ( aagey ( Mamar ki hadis ki tarah hai, us qaul tak : to Allah ne usey bakhsh diya aur unhon-ne billi ke waqiey (ke barey) mein aurat wali hadis ka zikr nahi kya aur Zubaidi ki hadis mein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne har cheez se, jisne us (jalaaey janey waley shakhs) ki koi bhi cheez li thi, farmaya : uska jo hissey terey paas hai pura wapas kar."
6984,"Shoba ne hamein Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aqba bin abdul-Ghaafir ko kehtey huey suna ke maine Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kar rahe they : tum se pahley ke logon mein se aik shakhs ko Allah Taala ne maal aur aulad se nawaza tha. us ne apne bachchon se kaha : har sura wahi kuchh karogey jiska main tumhen hukm de raha hun, ya main apna wirsa dusron ke sipurd kar doonga, jab main mar jaun to mujhey jalaa do. padhi. aur mujhey zyada ye lagta hai ke Qatada ne kaha, padhi. phir mujhey koot kar reza reza kar do, phir mujhey hawa mein uda do kyonke maine Allah ke yahan koi achai zakheera nahi ki. Allah mujh par poori qudrat rakhta hai ke mujhey azab de. kaha is ne un (apni aulad ( se pukhta ahad w paiman liya, to mere rab ki qism ! unhon-ne uske sath wahi kya (jo usne kaha tha. ( Allah Taala ne puchha : tum ne jo kuchh kya is par tumhen kis ne uksaaya? usne kaha : terey khof ne. farmaya : phir usey uske siwa (jo wo bhugat chuka tha, yani laash ka jalnaa aur Allah ke samney peshi wghaira) aur koi azab na hua."
6985,"Sulaiman , Sheban bin Abdur-Rehman aur abu-Awana sab ne Qatada se Shoba ki sanad ke sath usi ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya. Sheban aur abu-Awana ki hadis mein ye alfaz hain : logon mein se aik aadmi ko Allah Taala ne bahut maal aur aulad se nawaza aur tamimi ki hadis mein hai is ne Allah ke paas koi achai jama na karaai kaha ke Qatada ne uski ye tashreeh ki is ne Allah ke paas koi achai zakheera na ki. aur Sheban ki hadis mein hai : beshak us ne, Allah ki qism ! Allah ke yahan koi neki mehfooz na karaai aur abu-Awana ki hadis mein hai is ne kuchh jama na kya ( امتار ( Mim ke sath (ye sab bolney mein bhi miltey-jultey alfaz hain aur mana mein bhi.)"
6986,"Abdul-Aala bin Hammad ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Umra se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne rab azz-w-jall se naql kartey huey farmaya : aik bandey ne gunah kya, usne kaha : aey Allah ! mera gunah bakhsh de, to ( Allah ( tabarak w taala ne farmaya : mere bandey ne gunah kya hai, usko pata hai ke uska rab hai jo gunah maaf bhi karta hai aur gunah par giraft bhi karta hai, us bandey ne phir gunah kya to kaha : mere rab! mera gunah bakhsh de, to ( Allah ( tabarak w taala ne farmaya : mera banda hai, us ne gunah kya hai to usey malum hai ke uska rab hai jo gunah bakhsh deta hai aur (chahey to) gunah par pakadta hai. us bandey ne phir se wahi kya, gunah kya aur kaha : mere rab! mere liye mera gunah bakhsh de, to ( Allah ( tabarak w taala ne farmaya : mere bandey ne gunah kya to usey malum hai ke uska rab hai jo gunah bakhshta hai aur (chahey to) gunah par pakad leta hai, (mere bandey! ab tu) jo chahey kar, maine tujhey bakhsh diya hai. Abdul-Aala ne kaha : mujhey ( poori tarah) malum nahi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teesri baar farmaya ya chothi baar : jo chahey kar."
6987,Muhammad-bin zanjuwia qushairi ne kaha : hamein Abdul-Aala bin Hammad narsi ne isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki.
6988,"Hammam ne kaha : hamein Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Madina mein aik waaiz tha jisey Abdur-Rehman bin abi Umra kaha jata tha, maine usey kehtey huey suna ke maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : yaqinan aik bandey ne gunah kya ( aagey ( Hammaad-bin-Salma ki hadis ke mutabiq bayan kya aur us ne gunah kya (ke alfaz ( teen baar kahey aur teesri baar ke baad kaha : maine apne bandey ko bakhsh diya, lihaza jo chahey kare."
6989,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Amr-bin-Murra se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine abu-Ubaid ko Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waala Allah raat ko apna dast (rehmat bandon ki taraf) phaila deta hai taake din ko gunah karne wala tauba karey aur din ko apna dast (rehmat) phaila deta hai taake raat ko gunah karne wala tauba karey (aur wo us waqt tak yahi karta rahega ( yahan tak ke suraj maghrib se tuloo ho jaey."
6990,Abu-Dawud ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
6991,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Waeil ( Shaqiq ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala se badh kar koi nahi jisey madah ( uski rehmat w inayat ka iqrar aur is par uski tareef) pasand ho, isi liye usne khud apni madah farmai hai aur koi nahi jo Allah se badh kar ghairatmand ho, isi liye us ne be hayaai ke tamam kaam, unmein se jo zahir hain aur jo posheeda hain, haram kar diye hain."
6992,"Abdullah-bin-Numair aur abu-Muawia ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Shaqiq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah se badh kar koi ghayyoor nahi hai, isi liye us ne be-hayaai ke tamam kaam , unmein se jo zahir hain aur jo posheeda hain haram kar diye hain, Allah Taala se badh kar koi nahi hai jisey tareef zyada pasand ho."
6993,"Amr-bin-Murra ne kaha : maine abu-Waeil ko kehtey huey suna ke maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna, wo kehtey they. ( Amr-bin-Murra ne) kaha : maine un ( abu-Waeil ( se kaha : kya aap ne khud Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suna tha? unhon-ne kaha : haan aur unhon-ne usey marfooan bayan kiya :  Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah se badh kar koi ghairat mand nahi, isi liye us ne tamam khuli aur posheeda fawaahish (be-hayaai ki baatein) haram kar di aur Allah se badh kar kisi ko tareef pasand nahi (kyonke haqiqat mein wahi tareef ka haqdaar hai), isi liye us ne apni tareef farmai hai."
6994,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi nahi jisey Allah se badh kar tareef pasand ho, isi bina par us ne apni tareef farmai aur koi nahi jo Allah se badh kar ghairat mand ho. isi bina par us ne tamam fawaahish haram kar dien aur koi nahi jisey Allah se badh kar) bandon ka us se) ma'zirat karna pasand ho, isi bina par us ne kitab nazil farmai aur paighambaron ko bhejaa."
6995,"Hujjaj-bin-abi-Usman ne kaha : Yahya (bin-abi-kaseer) ne kaha : mujhey abu-Salma ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ghairat farmata hai aur be-shak momin bhi ghairat karta hai. Allah ki ghairat is baat par hoti hai ke momin aisey kaam karey jo usney is par haram kiya hai."
6996,"Yahya ne kaha : mujhey abu-Salma ne hadis bayan ki, unhein Urwa-bin-Zubair ne bayan kiya, unhein Hazrat Asma binte- abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye irshad farmatey huey suna : koi nahi jo izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah se zyada ghairat mand ho."
6997,"Abaan-bin-Yazeed aur harab-bin-Shaddad ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Hajjaj ki riwayat ki tarah sirf Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ki hadis ka zikr nahi kiya."
6998,"Hisham ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah se badh kar koi ghayyoor nahi hai."
6999,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-Muhammad ne Alaa se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Abdur-Rehman ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : momin (doosrey) momin ke liye ghairat karta hai (ke uski hurmat paamaal na ki jaey) aur Allah Taala to ghairat mein us se badh kar hai."
7000,Shoba ne kaha : maine Alaa ko isi sanad ke sath (yahi hadis bayan kartey huey) suna.
7001,"Yazeed ne kaha : hamein Taimi ne abu-Usman se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs ne aik aurat ko bosa diya, ( phir ( wo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur is waqiey ka zikr kya. tab (ye aayat ( nazil hui : din ke donon hisson aur raat ke kuchh hisson mein Namaz qaaim rakho, be-shak nekiyan buraaiyon ko door kar deti hain, ye yad dahaani hai yad rakhney walon ke liye. us shakhs ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! kya ye ( basharat ( sirf mere liye hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat mein se jo bhi) gunahon se paak honey ke liye) is par amal kare."
7002,"Moatamir ne apne walid ( Sulaiman Taimi ( se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu-Usman ne Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke aik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur us ne zikr kiya ke usne aik aurat ko bosa diya hai ya usko hath se chhuaa hai) ya aisa ( koi aur kaam kiya hai, maano ke wo iske kaffaarey ke mutaalliq sawal kar raha hai, kaha : tab izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne ye aayat nazil farmai, phir Yazeed ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
7003,"Jarir ne Sulaiman Taimi se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, kaha : aik shakhs ne aik aurat ke sath zina se kam darjey ka koi kaam kiya. wo Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya, unhon-ne iske samney usko bahut bada gunah qarar diya, phir wo Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya, unhon-ne bhi uske liye usko bahut badi baat qarar diya, phir wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, ( aagey ( Yazeed aur Moatamir ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
7004,"abu-Ahwas ne Samak se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Alqama aur Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya to usne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! maine Madina ke aakhiri hissey mein aik aurat ko qaabu kar liya aur iske alawa ke main us se hambistari karun maine us se aur sab kuchh hasil kar liya. to (ab) main aap ke samney hazir hun, aap mere barey mein jo chaahein faisla kar lein. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : Allah ne tumhara parda rakha , kaash! ! tum khud bhi apna parda rakhtey. (hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey koi jawab na diya. to ( kuchh der baad) wo shakhs utha aur chal diya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske peechhey aik aadmi bhej kar usey bulaya aur uske samney ye aayat padhi : din ke donon hisson aur raat ke kuchh hisson mein Namaz qaaim karo, be-shak nekiyan buraaiyon ko khatm kar deti hain. ye unke liye yad dihaani hai jo achi baat ko yad rakhney waley hain. is par logon mein se aik aadmi ne kaha : Allah ke Nabi ! kya ye khas usi ke liye hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya : balke tamam logon ke liye hai."
7005,"Shoba ne Samak-bin-Harab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Ibrahim ko apne maamun Aswad se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se abu-Ahwas ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki, unhon-ne apni hadis mein kaha : to Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! kya ye khas usi ke liye hai ya umumi taur par ham sab ke liye hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : balke tum sab ke liye aam hai."
7006,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! maine had ( lagney waley kaam ( jari hone wala kaam kar liya hai. mujh par had qaaim kijiye. (hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : (tab) Namaz ka waqt aa gaya, us ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi. jab Namaz padh li to kehney laga : Allah ke rasool ! maine had (ke qaabil gunah (ka kaam kiya hai, mere barey mein Allah ki kitab ka (jo ( faisla ( hai usey ( Nafiz (laagu) farmaiye . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya to hamarey sath Namaz mein shamil hua? usne kaha : haan , farmaya : tera gunah bakhsh diya gaya hai."
7007,"Shaddad ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hazrat abu Amama (Raziallahu anha) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : aik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif farma they aur ham bhi aap ke paas baithey huey they ke aik shakhs aaya to kehney laga : Allah ke rasool ! maine had (ke qaabil gunah (ka kaam kar diya hai. lihaza aap mujh par had qaaim kijiye . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh rahe, us ne dobara kaha : Allah ke rasool ! main had ka mustahiq ho gaya hun, aap mujh par had qaaim kijiye . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh rahe, us ne teesri baar ( yahi ( kaha to (us waqt) Namaz ki iqamat keh di gaee. Hazrat abu Amama (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz se ( farigh ho kar) wapas huey to wo shakhs aap ke peechhey chal padaa , main ( bhi) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey chal padaa ke dekhun Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usko kya jawab detey hain? wo shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ja mila aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! maine had (ke qaabil gunah (ka kaam kiya hai. aap mujh par had qaaim farmaein . Hazrat abu Amama (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se kaha : zara dekho : jab tum apne ghar se nikley they, to tum ne wuzu kiya tha aur achi tarah wuzu kiya tha? usne kaha : haan , Allah ke rasool ! ( achi tarah wuzu kiya tha. ( farmaya : iske baad tum ne hamarey sath Namaz padhi ? usne kaha : ji haan , Allah ke rasool ! (Hazrat abu Amama (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey farmaya : to yaqinan Allah Taala ne tumhari had . padhi. ya farmaya, padhi. tumharey gunah ko maaf kar diya hai."
7008,"Hisham ne Qatada se, unhon-ne abu-Siddeeq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum se pahley logon mein se aik shakhs tha us ne ninyaanwe qatl kiye, phir us ne zamin par basney walon mein se sabse badey aalim ke barey mein puchha (ke wo kon hai.) usey aik raahib ka pata bataya gaya. wo uske paas aaya aur puchha ke usne ninyaanwe qatl kiye hain, kya uske liye tauba (ki koi sabeel (rasta)) hai? usne kaha : nahi. to usne usey bhi qatl kar diya aur us (ke qatl ( se sau qatl poorey kar liye. us ne phir ahale-zameen mein se sabse badey aalim ke barey mein malum kiya. usey aik aalim ka pata bataya gaya. to usne ( ja kar) kaha is ne sau qatl kiye hain, kya uske liye tauba (ka imkan ( hai? us ( aalim ( ne kaha : haan, iske aur tauba ke darmyan kon haail (rukawet) ho sakta hai? tum falan-falan sarzameen par chaley jao. wahan ( aisey ( log hain jo Allah Taala ki ibadat kartey hain, tum bhi unke sath Allah ki ibadat mein mashghool ho jao aur apni sarzameen par wapas na aao, ye buri ( baton se bhari hui ( sarzameen hai. wo chal padaa , yahan tak ke jab aadha rasta tay kar liya to usey maut ne aa liya. uske barey mein rehmat ke Farishtey aur azab ke Farishtey jhagadney lagey. rehmat ke farishton ne kaha : ye shakhs tauba karta hua apne dil ko Allah ki taraf mutwajjeh karke aaya tha aur azab ke farishton ne kaha is ne kabhi neki ka koi kaam nahi kiya. to aik farishta aadmi ke roop mein unke paas aaya, unhon-ne usey apne darmyan (saalis (panch)) muqarrar kar liya. usne kaha : donon zaminon ke darmyan fasla maap lo, wo donon mein se jis zamin ke zyada qareeb ho to wo usi ( zamin ke logon ( mein se hoga. unhon-ne masafat ko maapaa to usey us zamin ke qareeb tar paya jiski taraf wo ja raha tha, chunanche rehmat ke farishton ne usey apne hathon mein ley liya. Qatada ne kaha : Hasan ( Basri) ne kaha : (is hadis mein) hamein bataya gaya ke jab usey maut ne aa liya tha to usne apne seeney se (ghaseet kar) khud ko (gunahon bhari zamin se) door kar liya tha."
7009,"Muaaz-bin-Muaaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Qatada se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu siddeeq naaji se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki : aik shakhs ne ninyaanwe insan qatl kiye, phir us ne ye poochhna shuru kar diya : kya uski tauba (ki koi sabeel) ho sakti hai? wo aik raahib ke paas aaya, us se puchha to usne jawab diya : terey liye koi tauba nahi. us ne us raahib ko (bhi) qatl kar diya. iske baad us ne phir se ( tauba ke mutaalliq ( poochhna shuru kar diya, phir aik basti se (doosri) basti ki taraf nikal padaa jis mein nek log rahtey they. wo rastey ke kisi hissey mein tha ke usey maut ne aan liya, wo (is waqt) apne seeney ke zariey se (pichhli gunahon bhari basti se) door hua, phir mar gaya. to uske barey mein rehmat ke farishton aur azab ke farishton ne aapas mein jhagdaa kya. to wo shakhs aik baalisht barabar nek basti ki taraf qareeb tha, usey us basti ke logon mein se ( shumaar) kar liya gaya."
7010,Shoba ne hamein Qatada se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki jis tarah Muaaz-bin-Muaaz ki hadis hai aur is mein mazeed ye kaha : to Allah ne us ( gunah gaaron ki basti) ko wahi kar di ke to door hoja aur us (nek logon ki basti) ko wahi kar di ke to qareeb ho jaa.
7011,"Talha bin Yahya ne abu-Barda se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab qiyamat ka din hoga to Allah Taala (eik marhaley par) har musalman ko aik Yahudi ya nasrani ata kar dega, phir farmaeyga : ye jahannam se tumharey liye chhutkaarey ka zaria banega."
7012,"Affaan-bin-Muslim ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hammam ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki ke Aun ( bin-Abdullah (aur Saeed bin abi burda ne unhein hadis bayan ki, wo donon abu-Burda ke samney maujood they jab wo Hazrat Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez ko apne walid se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jo musalman bhi faut hota hai Allah Taala uski jagah par aik Yahudi ya aik nasrani ko dozakh mein dakhil kar deta hai. kaha : Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez ne Hazrat abu-Burda ko teen baar us Allah ki qism di jiske siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi ke waqei unke walid ne unhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis bayan ki thi. unhon-ne un ( Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez (ke samney qism khaai. (Qatada ne) kaha : Saeed ne mujh se ye bayan nahi kya ke unhon-ne unse qism li aur na unhon-ne Aun ki (batai hui) baat par koi aetraz kya."
7013,"Abdus-Samad bin Abdul-Waris se riwayat hai, kaha : hamein Hammam ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne isi sanad ke sath Affaan ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur (Aun bin-Abdullah ki nisbat uske dada ki taraf kartey huey) kaha : Aun bin utba."
7014,"abu-Rawwad Harmi bin Umara ne kaha : hamein Shaddad abu Talha Raasbi ne Ghelaan bin Jarir se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Burda se, unhon-ne apne walid (Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din musalmanon mein se kuchh log pahadon jaisey (badey badey) gunah lekar aaeingey, Allah Taala unke liye wo gunah bakhsh dega, aur jahan tak main samajhta hun, wo un (gunahon) ko yahood aur nasara par daal dega. abu Rauh ne kaha : mujhey malum nahi ke ye shak kis ( rawi ( ki taraf se hai. Hazrat abu-Burda ne kaha : maine ye hadis Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez ko bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : kya tumharey walid ne tumhen ye hadis Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan ki thi? maine kaha : haan."
7015,"Qatada ne Safwan bin muharriz se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : aap ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se najwa (momin se Allah ki sargoshi) ke mutaalliq kis tarah suna tha? unhon-ne kaha : maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : momin ko qiyamat ke din uske rab azz-w-jall ke qareeb kya jaeyga, yahan tak ke Allah Taala is par apna parda daal dega (taake koi aur uske raaz par muttla na ho), phir us se iske gunahon ka iqrar karaaeyga aur farmaeyga : kya to (un sab gunahon ko) pehchanta hai? wo kahega : mere rab! main (un sab gunahon ko) pehchanta hun. ( Allah Taala ( farmaeyga : maine duniya main tum par) raham kartey huey) un gunahon ko chipa liya tha aur aaj (tum par raham kartey huey) tumharey liye un sab ko maaf karta hun, phir usey ( mahz ( uski nekiyon ka saheefa pakda diya jaeyga aur rahe kuffaar aur munaafeqeen to saari makhlooqat ke samney buland awaz se unhein kaha jaeyga : yahi hain jinhoney Allah par jhoot baandha."
7016,"Ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jihad kya Tabook ka (Tabook aik maqam ka naam hai Madina se pandarah manzil par Sham (Syria) ke raaste mein) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka irada tha Rome (mojooda Itly) aur Arab ke nasara ko dhamkaaney ka Sham (Syria) mein. Ibne-Shahab (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha : mujh se bayan kya Abdur-Rehman bin-Abdullah-bin Kab-bin-Malik ne unse bayan kya Abdullah-bin Kab ne jo Kab ko pakad kar chalaaya kartey they, unke beton mein se jab Kab ko aankhon se dikhaai dena band ho gaya tha, unhon-ne kaha : maine suna Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se, wo apna haal bayan kartey they, jab peechhey reh gaey they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jange-Tabook mein. saiyedna Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main kisi jihad main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey nahi raha siwaey jange-Tabook ke, albatta badr mein peechhey raha, par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi par ghussa nahi kya jo peechhey reh gaya tha aur badr main to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) musalmanon ke sath Quraish ka qaafila lotney ke liye nikley they lekin Allah ne musalmanon ko unke dushmanon se badha diya (aur qaafila nikal gaya) be waqt aur main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maujood tha lailatul-aqba main (lailatul-aqba wo raat hai jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar se bait li thi Islam par aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki madad karne par aur ye bait jamara Aqba ke paas jo Mina mein hai dobara hui. pehli baar mein baara Ansari they aur dusri baar mein 70 Ansari they) aur main nahi chahta ke us raat ke badley mein jange-badr mein Sharik hota bhale hi jange-badr logon mein us raat se zyada mashhoor hai (yani log usko afzal kehtey hain) aur mera qissa jange-Tabook se peechhey rehney ka ye hai ke jab ye jang hui to main sabse zyada taaqatwar aur maaldaar tha. Allah ki qism us se pahley mere paas 2 oontniyan kabhi nahi huin aur us ladai ke waqt mere paas 2 oontniyan thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us ladai ke liye chaley sakht garmi ke dinon main aur safar bhi lamba tha aur raah mein jangal they ( door dawaaz jin mein pani kam milta aur halaakat ka khof hota (aur muqaabla tha bahut dushmanon se, isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalmanon se waazeh taur par farma diya ke ''main us ladai ko jata hoon.'' ( halanke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ye aadat thi ke aur ladaaiyon mein apna irada saaf-saaf na farmatey maslihat se taake khabar mashhoor na ho (taake wo apni taiyaari kar lein. phir unse keh diya ke falan taraf unko jana padega, us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath bahut se musalman they aur koi daftar na tha, jis mein unke naam likhe hotey . saiyedna Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to aisey shakhs kam they jo ghayab rehna chahtey aur guman kartey ke ye Amr posheeda rahega jab tak Allah paak ki taraf se koi wahi na utrey aur ye jihad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt kya jab phal paak gaey they aur saaya khub tha, aur mujhey un chizon ka bahut shauq tha. aakhir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne taiyaari ki aur musalmanon ne bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath taiyaari ki maine bhi subah ko nikalna shuru kya is irade se ke main bhi unke sath taiyaari karun lekin har roz main lot aata aur kuchh faisla na karta aur apne dil mein ye kehta ke main jab chaahoon ja sakta hun, (kyonke saman safar ka mere paas maujood tha) yun hi hota raha, yahan tak ke log barabar koshish kartey rahe aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi subah ke waqt nikley aur musalman bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley aur maine koi taiyaari nahi ki. phir subah ko main nikla aur lot kar aa gaya aur koi faisla nahi kya, yahi haal raha yahan tak ke logon ne jaldi ki aur sab mujaahideen aagey nikal gaey, us waqt maine bhi kooch ka irada kya ke unse mil jaun to kash! main aisa karta lekin meri taqdeer mein na tha baad iske jab bahar nikalta Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke janey ke baad to mujh ko ranj hota kyonke main koi pairwi ke laaiq na paata magar aisa shakhs jis par munafiq honey ka guman tha ya mazoor, zaeef aur kamzor logon mein se, khair Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne raah mein meri yad kahin na ki yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Tabook mein pahunchey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon mein baithey huey they us waqt farmaya : '' Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kahan gaya?'' eik shakhs bola : bani Salma mein se ya Rasulullah ! uski chaadaron ne usko rok rakha , wo apne donon kinaron ko dekhta hai (yani apne libaas aur nafs mein mashghool aur masroof hai). saiyedna Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye sun kar kaha : tuney buri baat kahi , Allah ki qism ya Rasulullah ! ham to Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko achchha samajhtey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye sun kar chup ho rahe, itney mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko dekha jo safaid kapdey pahney huey aa raha tha aur ret ko uda raha tha (chalney ki wjah se) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''abu-Khaisma hai.'' phir wo abu-Khaisma hi tha aur abu-Khaisma wo shakhs tha jisne aik saa khajoor sadqa di thi jab munaafiqon ne is par tana kya tha. saiyedna Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab mujhey khabar pahunchi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Tabook se lautey Madina ki taraf to mera ranj badh gaya. maine jhoot baatein banaanaa shuru kiin ke koi baat aisi kahun jis se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ghussa mit jaey kal ke roz aur us Amr ke liye maine har aik aqlmand shakhs se madad lena shuru ki apne ghar walon mein se yani unse bhi salaah li (ke kya baat bataaun) jab logon ne mujh se bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qareeb aa pahunchey us waqt Sara jhoot kaafoor ho gaya aur main samajh gaya ke ab koi jhoot bana kar main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se najat nahi paaney ka, aakhir maine niyat kar li sach bolney ki, aur subah ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar se aatey to pahley masjid mein jatey aur 2 rakatein padhtey, phir logon se milney ke liye baithtey. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye kar chukey to jo log peechhey reh gaey they, unhon-ne apne uzr bayan karne shuru kiye aur qasmein khaney lagey aisey assi (80) se zyada chand aadmi they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki zahir ki baat ko maan liya aur unse bait ki aur unke liye dua ki maghfirat ki aur unki niyat (yani dil ki baat ko) Allah ke sipurd kya, yahan tak ke main bhi aaya jab maine salam kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tabassum kya lekin wo tabassum jaisey ghusse ki haalat mein kartey hain, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aa!'' main chalta hua aaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney betha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tu kyon peechhey reh gaya tu ney to sawari bhi khareed li thi.'' maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! agar main aap ke siwa kisi aur shakhs ke paas duniya ke logon mein se baithta to main ye khayal karta ke koi uzr bayan karke iske ghussa se nikal jaaunga aur mujhey Allah Taala ne zaban ki quwwat di hai (yani mein umda taqreer kar sakta hun aur khub baat bana sakta hun) lekin qism Allah ki main janta hun ke agar main koi jhoot baat aap se keh dun aur aap khush ho jayen mujh se to qareeb hai Allah Taala aapko mere uper ghussa kar dega (yani Allah Taala Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko batla dega ke mera uzr ghalat aur jhoot tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) naraz ho jaeinge) aur agar main aap se sach sach kahunga to beshak aap ghussa hongey lekin mujhey ummeed hai ke Allah Taala iska anjam b-khair karega. Allah ki qism ! mujhey koi uzr na tha. Allah ki qism ! main kabhi na itna taaqatwar tha, na itna maaldaar tha jitna us waqt tha jab aap se peechhey reh gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Kab ne sach kaha, '' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : '' achchha ja yahan tak ke Allah hukm de terey barey mein.'' main khada hua aur chand log bani-Salma ke daud kar mere peechhey huey aur mujh se kehney lagey : Allah ki qism ! ham nahi jantey tum ko tuney is se pahley koi qasoor kya ho, to tum aajiz kyon ho gaey aur koi uzr kyon na kar diya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney jaisey aur logon ne jo peechhey reh gaey they uzr bayan kiye aur tera gunah mitaaney ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka istighfar kafi tha, Allah ki qasam! wo log mujh ko malaamat karne lagey yahan tak ke maine irada kya phir lotun Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aur apne taiin jhoota karun aur koi uzr bayan karun. phir maine un logon se kaha : kisi aur ka bhi aisa haal hua hai jo mera hua hai. unhon-ne kaha : haan 2 log aur hain, unhon-ne bhi wahi kaha : jo tuney kaha : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse bhi wahi farmaya jo tujh se farmaya, maine puchha : wo 2 log kon hain? unhon-ne kaha : Muraara bin Rabee aur Hilal bin Umayya waaqifi (Raziallahu anhu). un logon ne aisey 2 shakhson ka naam liya jo nek they aur badr ki ladai mein maujood they aur pairwi ke qaabil they jab un logon ne un donon shakhson ka naam liya to main chala gaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalmanon ko mana kar diya tha ke ham teenon aadmiyon se koi baat na karey, un logon mein se jo peechhey reh gaey they, to logon ne ham se parhez shuru kya aur unka haal hamarey sath bilkul badal gaya yahan tak ke zamin bhi maano badal gaee wo zamin hi na rahi jisko main pehchanta tha pachaas raaton tak hamara yahi haal raha mere donon sathi to aajiz ho gaey aur apne gharon mein baith rahe rotey huey lekin main to sab logon mein kam-umr aur zor daar tha, main nikla karta tha aur Namaz ke liye bhi aata aur bazaron mein bhi phirtaa par koi shakhs mujh se baat na karta aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aata aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam karta aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni jagah baithey hotey Namaz ke baad aur dil mein ye kehta ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne labon ko hilaaya, salam ka jawab dene ke liye ya nahi hilaaya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb Namaz padhta aur daz-deeda nazar se (kankhiyon se) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekhta, to jab main Namaz mein hota Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri taraf dekhtey aur jab main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf dekhta to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) munh pher letey yahan tak ke jab musalmanon ki sakhti mujh par lambi hui to main chala aur abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ke baagh ki diwar par chadha. abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) mere chacha zaad bhai they aur sab logon se zyada mohabbat mujhey unse thi, unko salam kya, to Allah ki qism unhon-ne salam ka jawab tak na diya ( Subhan-Allah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke taabe aisey hotey hain ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke irshad ke samney bhai betey ki marawwat bhi nahi kartey jab tak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aisi mohabbat na ho to eman kis kaam ka hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis jab malum ho jaey ke sahi hai to mujtahid aur maulwiyon ka qaul jo uske khilaf ho diwar par maarna chahiye aur hadis par chalna chahiye) maine unse kaha : aey abu-Qataada! main tum ko qism deta hun Allah ki tum ye nahi jantey ke main Allah aur uske rasool se mohabbat rakhta hun, wo khamosh rahe, phir teesri baar qism di to boley : Allah aur uska rasool khub janta hai ye bhi Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se nahi boley balke khud apne mein baat ki aakhir meri aankhon se aansu nikal padey aur main peeth mod kar chala aur diwar par chadha. main Madina ke bazar mein ja raha tha to aik kisaan Sham (Syria) ke kisaanon mein se jo Madina main anaaj bechney ke liye aaya tha, kehney laga : Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ka ghar mujh ko kon bataaeyga? logon ne usko ishara shuru kya yahan tak ke wo mere paas aaya aur mujhey aik khat diya Ghassaan ke badshah ka, main munshi tha, maine usko padha, usmein ye likha tha, baad hamd w naat ke Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ko malum ho ke ham ko ye khabar pahunchi hai ke tumharey sahib ne yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tujh par jafaa ki hai aur Allah Taala ne tum ko zillat ke ghar mein nahi kya na us jagah jahan tumhara haq zaaye ho to tum ham se mil jao ham tumhari khaatir daari karengey. maine jab ye khat padha to kaha : ye bhi aik bila hai aur us khat ko maine choolhey mein jalaa diya. jab pachaas din mein se chalis (40) din guzar gaey aur wahi na aai to achcha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka paigham laney wala mere paas aaya aur kehney laga : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tum ko hukm kartey hain ke apni biwi se alehda raho maine kaha : main usko talaaq de dun ya kya karun? wo bola : nahi talaaq mat do sirf alag raho aur us se sohbat mat karo aur mere donon sathiyon ke paas bhi yahi payaam gaya. maine apni bevi se kaha : to apne azeezon mein chali ja aur wahin reh yahan tak ke Allah Taala is mamley mein koi hukm de. Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi ye sun kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas gaee aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) aik boodha bekar shakhs hai uske paas koi khaadim bhi nahi to kya aap bura samajhtey hain agar main uski khidmat kya karun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main khidmat ko bura nahi samajhta, lekin wo tujh se sohbat na kare.'' wo boli : Allah ki qism ! usko kisi kaam ka khayal nahi aur Allah ki qism ! wo us din se ab tak ro raha hai. mere ghar walon ne kaha : kash! tum bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apni biwi ke paas rehney ki ijazat ley lo kyonke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ki aurat ko uski khidmat karne ki ijazat di. maine kaha : main kabhi ijazat na loonga Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apni bevi ke liye aur malum nahi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kya farma dengey, agar main ijazat loon apni biwi ke liye aur main jawan aadmi hun. phir das raaton tak mein usi haal mein raha yahan tak ke pachaas raatein poori huin, us taareekh se jab se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana kya tha ham se baat karne se phir pachaaswin raat ko subah ke waqt maine Namaz padhi apne ghar ki chhat par. mein usi haal mein betha tha jo Allah Taala ne hamara haal bayan kya ke mera ji tang ho gaya tha aur zamin mujh par tang ho gaee thi bawajud ye ke itni kushada hai. itney mein maine aik pukarney waley ki awaz suni jo Sala par chadha (Sala aik pahaad hai Madina mein) aur buland awaz se pukara : aey Kab-bin-Malik! khush ho jaa. ye sun kar main sajde mein gira aur maine pehchaana ke khushi aai, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko khabar ki ke Allah ne ham ko maaf kya, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr ki Namaz padh chukey. log chaley ham ko khushkhabri dene ke liye to mere donon sathiyon ke paas chand khushkhabri dene waley gaey aur aik shakhs ne mere paas ghoda daudaaya aur aik daudney wala douda Aslam ke qabeeley se meri taraf aur uski awaz ghodey se jald mujh ko pahunchi. jab wo shakhs aaya jiski awaz maine suni thi khushkhabri ki to maine apne donon kapdey utaarey aur usko pehna diye, uski khushkhabri ke sile mein. Allah ki qasam! us waqt mere paas wahi 2 kapdey they. maine 2 kapdey udhaar liye aur unko pehna aur chala Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se milney ki niyat se. log mujh se miltey jatey they giroh giroh aur mujh ko Mubarak baad detey jatey they maafi ki aur kehtey they : Mubarak ho tum ko Allah ki maafi ki tumharey liye yahan tak ke main masjid mein pahuncha . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein baithey they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas log they. Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) mujh ko dekhtey hi khadey huey aur daudey yahan tak ke musaafa kya mujh se aur mujh ko mubaarkbaad di. Allah ki qism ! muhajireen mein se unke siwa koi shakhs khada nahi hua, to Kab (Raziallahu anhu) Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke us ehsan ko nahi bhooltey they. saiyedna Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak khushi se chamak damak raha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khush ho ja aaj ka din jo terey liye behtar din hai, jab se teri maan ne tujh ko janaa.'' maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ye maafi aap ki taraf se hai ya Allah ki taraf se? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki taraf se.'' aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab khush ho jatey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra chamak jata maano chaand ka aik tukda hai aur ham is baat ko pehchan letey (yani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khushi ko) jab main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney betha to maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! meri maafi ki khushi mein main apne maal ko sadqa kar dun Allah aur uske rasool ke liye? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : '' thoda maal apna rakh ley. '' maine arz kya : to main apna hissey khaibar ka rakh leta hun aur maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aakhir sachchai ne mujhey nijat di aur meri tauba mein ye bhi dakhil hai ke hamesha sach kahunga jab tak zinda rahun. Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! main nahi janta ke Allah Taala ne kisi musalman par aisa ehsan kya ho sach bolney mein jab se maine ye zikr kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jaisa umda andaz se mujh par ehsan kya, Allah ki qism ! maine us waqt se koi jhoot qasdan nahi bola : jab se ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha, aaj ke din tak aur mujhey ummeed hai ke Allah Taala baqi zindagi mein bhi mujh ko jhoot se bachaaeyga. Kab ne kaha : Allah Taala ne ye aayatein utaarin لَّقَد تَّابَ اللَّهُ عَلَى النَّبِيِّ وَالْمُهَاجِرِينَ وَالْأَنصَارِ الَّذِينَ اتَّبَعُوهُ فِي سَاعَةِ الْعُسْرَةِ مِن بَعْدِ مَا كَادَ يَزِيغُ قُلُوبُ فَرِيقٍ مِّنْهُمْ ثُمَّ تَابَ عَلَيْهِمْ إِنَّهُ بِهِمْ رَءُوفٌ رَّحِيمٌ ( ١١٧ ( وَعَلَى الثَّلَاثَةِ الَّذِينَ خُلِّفُوا حَتَّىٰ إِذَا ضَاقَتْ عَلَيْهِمُ الْأَرْضُ بِمَا رَحُبَتْ وَضَاقَتْ عَلَيْهِمْ أَنفُسُهُمْ وَظَنُّوا أَن لَّا مَلْجَأَ مِنَ اللَّـهِ إِلَّا إِلَيْهِ ثُمَّ تَابَ عَلَيْهِمْ لِيَتُوبُوا إِنَّ اللَّهَ هُوَ التَّوَّابُ الرَّحِيمُ ( ١١٨ ( يَا أَيُّهَا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا اتَّقُوا اللَّہَ وَكُونُوا مَعَ الصَّادِقِينَ ( ١١٩ )( التوبة : 117 - ۱۱۹ ( yani ''be shak Allah Taala ne maaf kya Nabi aur muhajireen aur Ansar ko jinhoney sath diya Nabi ka muflisi ke waqt.'' yahan tak ke farmaya : ''wo meharban hai raham wala aur Allah Taala ne maaf kya un teen shakhson ko jo peechhey daley gaey yahan tak ke jab zamin un par tang ho gaee bawajud kushadgi ke aur unke ji bhi tang ho gaey aur samjhey ke ab koi bachao nahi Allah se magar usi ki taraf phir Allah ne maaf kya unko taake wo tauba karein beshak Allah Taala bakhshney wala meharban hai. aey eman waalo! daro Allah Taala se aur sath raho sachchon ke.'' Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! Allah Taala ne us se badh kar koi ehsan mujh par nahi kya baad Islam ke jo itna bada ho mere nazdeek is baat se ke maine sach bol diya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur jhoot nahi bola, warna tabah hota jaisey jhootey tabah huey. Allah Taala ne jhooton ki jab wahi utari to aisi burai ki ke kisi ki na ki to farmaya : ( سَيَحْلِفُونَ بِاللَّهِ لَكُمْ إِذَا انقَلَبْتُمْ إِلَيْهِمْ لِتُعْرِضُوا عَنْهُمْ فَأَعْرِضُوا عَنْهُمْ إِنَّهُمْ رِجْسٌ وَمَأْوَاهُمْ جَهَنَّمُ جَزَاءً بِمَا كَانُوا يَكْسِبُونَ ( ٩٥ ( يَحْلِفُونَ لَكُمْ لِتَرْضَوْا عَنْهُمْ فَإِن تَرْضَوْا عَنْهُمْ فَإِنَّ اللَّهَ لَا يَرْضَىٰ عَنِ الْقَوْمِ الْفَاسِقِينَ ( ٩٦ ( ) التوبة : 95 - ۹۶ ( ) ''jab tum lot kar aaey to qasmein khaney lagey taake tum kuchh na bolo un se, so na bolo unse wo napak hain, unka thikana jahannam hai ye badla hai unki kamaai ka qasmein khaatey hain tum se ke tum khush ho jao un se. so agar tum khush ho jao unse tab bhi Allah Taala khush nahi hoga badkaaron se.'' saiyedna Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham peechhey daley gaey teenon aadmi un logon se jinka uzr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabool kya jab unhon-ne qism khaai to bait ki unse aur istighfar kya unke liye aur ham ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne daal rakha (yani hamara muqaddima daal rakha) yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne faisla kya, usi sabab se Allah Taala ne farmaya ke ''maaf kya un teenon ko jo peechhey reh gaey aur us lafz se (yani ( خُلِّفُوْا ( se) ye murad nahi hai ke ham jihad se peechhey reh gaey balke murad wahi hai hamarey muqaddima ka peechhey rehna aur daal rakhna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka usko ba-nisbat un logon ke jinhoney qism khaai aur uzr kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabool kya unke uzr ko."
7017,Uqail ne ibne-Shahab se Yunus ki sanad ke sath Zohri se bilkul isi tarah riwayat ki.
7018,"Zohri ke bhatijey Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Muslim ne hamein apne chacha Muhammad-bin Muslim Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Abdur-Rehman bin-Abdullah-bin Kab-bin-Malik ne khabar di ke Abdullah-bin Kab-bin-Malik ne, aur wo Hazrat Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ke naa-beena honey ke baad unka hath pakad kar unki rehnumai kartey they, kaha : maine Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo apni hadis ( apna waqia ( bayan kartey they jab wo jange-Tabook main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se peechhey reh gaey they, phir unhon-ne (pichhli hadis ki tarah) hadis bayan ki aur is mein Yunus ki riwayat par mazeed ye kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kam hi kisi ghazwey ka irada farmatey they magar amalan us jang ke honey tak, kisi aur (muhim) ki jahat zahir farmatey yahan tak ke ye jang ( bhi usi nahaj par) hua aur unhon-ne Zohri ke bhatijey ki hadis mein abu-Khaisma ka aur unke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ja milney ka zikr nahi kya."
7019,"Maaqil bin Ubaidullah ne Zohri se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Abdur-Rehman bin-Abdullah-bin Kab-bin-Malik ne apne chacha Ubaidullah bin Kab se riwayat ki aur jab Hazrat Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ki aankhen jati rahen to wahi unka hath pakad kar unki rehnumai kartey they. wo apni qaum mein sabse badey aalim aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ki hadison ke sabse badey Hafiz they, unhon-ne kaha : maine apne walid Hazrat Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo un teen logon mein se aik they jinki tauba qabool ki gaee, wo hadis bayan kartey they ke wo 2 jangon ko chhod kar kabhi kisi ghazwey mein jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne lada, aap se peechhey nahi rahe. unhon-ne (pichhli hadis ki tarah) hadis bayan ki aur is mein kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ki bahut badi tadaad ke sath, jo das hazaar se zyada they aur kisi mehfooz rakhney waley ke diwan (rajister) mein un sab ke naam darj na they, us jang ke liye nikley."
7020,"Saeed bin Musaiyab aur Urwa-bin-Zubair aur Alqama bin Waqas aur Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah-bin Utba-bin- Masood se riwayat hai, un sab logon ne Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki hadis riwayat ki jab un par tohmat ki tohmat karne walon ne aur kaha : jo kaha, phir Allah Taala ne paak kya unko unki tohmat se. Zohri ne kaha : un sab logon ne eik-eik tukda us hadis ka mujh se riwayat kya aur kuchh unmein se zyada yad rakhney waley they us hadis ko kuchh se aur zyada Hafiz they aur umda bayan karne waley they usko aur maine yad rakhi har aik se jo riwayat suni aur kuchh ki hadis kuchh ki tasdeeq karti hai. un logon ne bayan kya ke Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab safar ka irada kartey to Qura daltey apni aurton par aur jis aurat ke naam par Qura nikalta, usko safar mein sath ley jatey. Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Qura daala aik jihad ke safar mein usmein mera naam nikla. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath gaee aur ye zikr us waqt ka hai jab parde ka hukm utar chuka tha main apne hodaj mein sawar hoti aur raah mein jab utarti to bhi usi hodaj mein rehti. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jihad se farigh huey aur lautey aur Madina se qareeb ho gaey. aik baar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne raat ko kooch ka hukm diya, main khadi hui jab logon ne kooch ki khabar kar di aur chali, yahan tak ke lashkar ke aagey badh gaee, jab main apne kaam se farigh hui to apne hodaj ki taraf aai aur Sina ko chhuwa, malum hua ke mera haar zifaar ke nageenon ka gir gaya, (zifaar aik gaaun hai Yaman mein) mein lauti aur us haar ko dhoondney lagi uske dhoondney mein mujhey der lagi aur wo log aa pahunchey jo mera hodaj uthatey they, unhon-ne wo uthaya aur mere oont par rakh diya jis par main sawar hoti thi wo ye samjhey ke main usi hodaj mein hun. us waqt auratein halki ( dubli) thin na sandhi thin na moti kyonke thoda khana khaati thin, isliye unko hodaj ka bojh aadat ke khilaf malum na hua, jab unhon-ne usko oont par laada aur uthaya, aur main aik kam-umr ladki bhi thi, aakhir logon ne oont ko uthaya, aur chal diye aur maine apna haar us waqt paya jab Sara lashkar chal diya, main jo unke thikaaney par aai to wahan na kisi ki awaz hai, na koi awaz sunney wala hai, maine ye irada kya ke jahan baithi thi wahin baith jaun aur main ye samjhi ke log jab mujhey na paeingey , to yahin lot kar aaeingey , to main usi thikaaney par baithi thi, itney mein meri aankh lag gaee aur main so rahi , aur Safwan bin muattal Salma zakwaani (Raziallahu anhu) aik shakhs tha, wo aaraam ke liye aakhir raat mein lashkar ke peechhey thehra tha, jab wo rawaana hua to subah ko mere thikaaney par pahuncha, usko aik aadmi ka jussa malum hua, jo so raha hai, wo mere paas aaya aur mujh ko pehchan liya dekhtey hi, isliye ke main parde ka hukm utarney se pahley iske samney hua karti. main jaag uthi, uski awaz sun kar jab us ne ( إِنَّا لِلَّـهِ وَإِنَّا إِلَيْهِ رَاجِعُونَ ( padha mujh ko pehchan kar. maine apna munh dhanp liya apni odhni se. Allah ki qasam! us ne koi baat mujh se nahi ki, na maine uski koi baat suni siwaey (( إِنَّا لِلَّـهِ وَإِنَّا إِلَيْهِ رَاجِعُون ( kehney ke. phir us ne apna oont bithaya aur apna hath mere chadhney ke liye bichhaa diya. main oont par Sawar ho gaee aur wo paidal chala oont ko kheenchta hua, yahan tak ke ham lashkar mein pahunchey aur lashkar ke log utar chukey they sakht do-pahar ki garmi mein, to mere muqaddmey mein tabah huey, jo log tabah huey (yani jinhoney bad-gumaani ki) aur Quran mein jiski nisbat ( تَوَلَّى كِبْرَه ( aaya hai yani baani-mabaani us tohmat ka wo Abdullah-bin-Ubai bin salool (munafiq tha). aakhir ham Madina mein aaey aur main jab Madina mein pahunchi to bimar ho gaee aik mahina tak bimar rahi aur logon ka ye haal tha ke bohtan karne walon ki baton mein ghaur kartey aur mujhey unki kisi baat ki khabar na thi. Mina sirf mujh ko is baat se shak hua ke maine apni bimari main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wo shafqat na dekhi thi, jo pahley mere haal par hoti. jab main bimar hui Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sirf andar aatey aur salam kartey phir farmatey : ''ye aurat kaisi hai.'' so is baat se mujhey shak hota lekin mujhey us kharabi ki khabar na thi, yahan tak ke jab main dubli ho gaee bimari janey ke baad to main nikli aur mere sath mistah ki maan bhi nikli manaase ki taraf (manaase jagah thi Madina ke bahar) aur wo pakhaney ki jagah thi ham logon ke (paakhaaney banney se pahley) ham log raat hi ko nikla kartey aur raat hi ko chaley aatey aur ye zikr us waqt ka hai jab hamarey gharon ke nazdeek pakhaney nahi baney they aur ham pahley Arbon ki tarah jangal mein jaya kartey (paakhaaney ke liye) aur ghar ke paas pakhaney banaaney se nafrat rakhtey, to main chali aur Umme- mistah mere sath thi wo beti thi abu-Raham bin matlab bin abd munaaf ki aur uski maan sakhr bin Aamir ki beti thi jo khala thi saiyedna Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ki (iska naam Salma tha) uske betey ka naam mistah bin Asaasa bin Ibad bin Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) tha, gharaz main aur Umme- Mistah donon jab apne kaam se farigh ho chukein to wapas apne ghar ki taraf aa rahi thin, itney mein umme-Mistah ka paon uljhaa apni chadar main aur boli: halaak hua mistah . maine kaha : tuney buri baat kahi. to bura kehti hai us shakhs ko jo badr ki ladai mein Sharik tha. wo boli: aey naadaan ! tuney kuchh nahi suna. Mistah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kya kaha? maine kaha : kya kaha is ne mujh se bayan kya jo bohtan lagaaney walon ne kaha tha. ye sun kar meri bimari badh gaee, aik aur bimari badhai. main jab apne ghar pahunchi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar tashrif laey aur salam kya aur farmaya : ''ab us aurat ka kya haal hai?'' maine kaha : aap mujh ko ijazat detey hain apne maan-baap ke paas janey ki. aur mera us waqt ye irada tha ke main maan-baap ke paas ja kar us khabar ki tehqeeq karun. aakhir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh ko ijazat di aur main apne maan-baap ke paas aai. maine apni maan se kaha : ammaan! ye log kya bak rahe hain. wo boli: beta ! to uska khayal na kar aur usko badi baat mat samajh Allah ki qism aisa bahut kam hua hai ke kisi mard ke paas aik khoobsurat aurat ho jo usko chahta ho aur uski saukanein bhi hon aur saukanein uske aib na nikaalein. maine kaha : Subhan-Allah ! logon ne to ye kehna shuru kar diya. main saari raat roti rahi. subah tak mere aansu na thahrey, aur na neend aai subah ko bhi mein ro rahi thi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saiyedna Ali-bin abi-Talib aur saiyedna Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya kyonke wahi nahi utri thi aur un donon se mashwara liya mujh ko juda karne ke liye (yani talaaq dene ke liye) saiyedna Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne to wahi raey di jo wo jantey they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi ke haal ko aur uski ismat ko aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mohabbat ko iske sath. Mina unhon-ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aap ki bevi hain aur ham to siwa behtri ke aur koi baat uski nahi jantey. saiyedna Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah Taala ne aap par tangi nahi ki aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke siwa auratein bahut hain aur agar aap londi se poochhiye to wo aap se sach keh degi (laundi se murad Barira hai jo Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas rehti thi) Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Barira ko bulaya aur farmaya : ''aey Bareera! tu ney kabhi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aisi baat dekhi hai jis se tujh ko uski paakdaamni mein shak padey?'' Barira ne kaha : qism uski jisne aapko sachcha paighambar karke bheja hai agar main unka koi kaam dekhti kabhi to main aib bayan karti. is se zyada koi aib nahi hai ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kam Umr ladki hai, aata chhod kar ghar ka so jati hai, phir bakri aati hai aur usko kha leti hai. ( matlab ye hai ke unmein koi aib nahi jis ko aap poochhtey hain na iske siwa koi aib hai jo aib hai wo yahi hai ke bholi bhaali ladki aur kam umri ki wjah se ghar ka bando-bast nahi kar sakti) Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par khadey huey aur Abdullah-bin-Ubai salool se badla chaha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya member par : ''aey musalman logo! kon badla lega mera us shakhs se jiski sakht baat eza dene wali mere ghar walon ki nisbat mujh tak pahunchi. Allah ki qasam! main to apni ghar wali (yani Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko) nek samajhta hun aur jis shakhs se ye log tohmat lagaatey hain (yani Safwan bin muattal (Raziallahu anhu) se) usko bhi nek samajhta hun aur wo kabhi mere ghar mein nahi gaya magar mere sath.'' ye sun kar saiyedna Sad-bin-Muaz Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) (jo qabila Aus ke sardaar they) khadey huey aur kehney lagey : ya Rasulullah! main aap ka badla leta hun. agar tohmat karne wala hamari qaum Aus mein se hai to ham uski gardan maartey hain aur jo hamarey bhaiyon khazraj mein se hai to aap hukm kijiye ham aap ke hukm ki tameel karengey (yani uski gardan maarengey) ye sun kar saiyedna Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur wo khazraj qabeele ke sardaar they aur nek aadmi they lekin us waqt unko apni qaum ki hamiiyat aa gaee aur kehney lagey : aey Sad-bin-Muaz! qism Allah ki baqa ki, to hamari qaum ke shakhs ko qatl na karega, na kar sakega. ye sun kar Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) jo Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ke chachazaad bhai they khadey huey aur Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) se kehney lagey : tuney ghalat kaha : qism Allah ki baqaa ki! ham usko qatl karengey aur to munafiq hai jab to munaafiqon ki taraf se ladta hai. gharaz ke donon qabeeley Aus aur khazraj ke log uth khadey huey aur qareeb tha ke kusht w khoon shuru ho aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par khadey huey they unko samjha rahe they aur unka ghussa faro kar rahe they yahan tak ke wo khamosh ho gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi khamosh ho rahe. Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : main us din bhi Sara din roti rahi ke mere aansu na thamtey they aur na neend aati thi, phir dusri raat bhi roti rahi ke na aansu thamtey they, na neend aati thi aur mere bap ne ye guman kya ke rotey-rotey mera kalejaa phat jaeyga mere maan-baap mere paas baithey they aur main ro rahi thi, itney mein Ansar ki aik aurat ne ijazat mangi . maine usko ijazat di wo bhi aa kar roney lagi, phir ham usi haalat mein they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur salam kya aur baithey aur jis roz se mujh par tohmat hui thi us roz se aaj tak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas nahi baithey they aur aik mahina yunhi guzra tha mere muqaddime mein koi wahi nahi utri. Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tashahud padha baithtey hi aur farmaya : aey Aaisha! mujhko tumhari taraf se aisi-aisi khabar pahunchi hai, phir agar tum paakdaaman ho to an-qareeb Allah Taala tumhari paakdaamni bayan kar dega aur agar tuney gunah kya hai to tauba kar aur bakhshish maang Allah se us waastey ke banda jab gunah ka iqrar karta hai aur tauba karta hai Allah usko bakhsh deta hai.'' Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni baat tamam kar chukey to mere aansu bilkul band ho gaey yahan tak ke aik qatra bhi na raha. maine apne bap se kaha : aap jawab dein meri taraf se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us muqaddime mein jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, mere bap boley : Allah ki qism mein nahi janta kya main jawab dun Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko) Subhan-Allah bap to muhibbe-rasool they bhale hi unki beti ka muqaddima tha par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney dam na maara). maine apni maan se kaha : tum jawab do meri taraf se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko . wo boli : Allah ki qism mein nahi janti kya jawab dun Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko . aakhir maine khud hi kaha aur main kam-umr ladki thi maine Quran nahi padha hai lekin main qism Allah ki ye janti hun ke tum logon ne is baat ko yahan tak suna ke tumharey dil mein jam gaee aur tum ne usko sach samajh liya (ye Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne ghussey se farmaya, warna sach kisi ne nahi samjha, bajuz tohmat karne walon ke) phir agar tum se kahun mein be-gunah hun aur Allah Taala janta hai ke main be-gunah hun to bhi tum mujh ko sachcha nahi manney ke, aur agar main aik gunah ka iqrar kar loon jisko maine nahi kya hai aur Allah Taala janta hai ke main usse paak hun to tum mujh ko sachcha samjhogey aur main apni aur tumhari misl siwaey iske koi nahi paati jo Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke bap ki thi (Yaqoob (Alaihissalam) ki aur Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko ranj mein unka naam yad na aaya Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ka bap kaha) jab unhon-ne kaha : (فَصَبْرٌ جَمِيلٌ وَاللَّهُ الْمُسْتَعَانُ عَلَى مَا تَصِفُونَ) yani ab sabr behtar hai aur tumhari us guftgu par Allah hi ki madad darkaar hai, phir maine karwat mod li aur main apne bichhoney par let rahi aur main Allah ki qism us waqt janti thi ke main paak hun aur Allah Taala zaroor meri paaki zahir karega lekin Allah ki qism mujhey ye guman na tha ke meri shaan mein Quran utrega jo padha jaeyga (qiyamat tak) kyonke meri shaan khud mere guman mein is laaiq na thi ke Allah izzat aur buzurgi wala mere muqaddime mein kalam karey aur kalam bhi aisa jo padha jaey albatta mujh ko ye ummeed thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khuwab mein koi mazmoon aisa dekhengey jis se Allah Taala meri paaki zahir kar dega. Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : to Allah ki qism Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni jagah se nahi uthey they aur na ghar walon mein se koi bahar gaya tha ke Allah Taala ne apne paighambar (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi bheji aur utara Quran ko. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wahi ki sakhti malum honey lagi yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke jism Mubarak par se mauta ki tarah pasiney ke qatrey tapakney lagey, jaadon ke dinon mein us kalam ki sakhti se jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par utra (is liye ke badey shehanshaah ka kalam tha) jab ye haalat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jati rahi (yani wahi khatm ho chuki) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hansney lagey aur awwal Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye kalima munh se nikala. farmaya : ''aey Aaisha! khush hoja Allah Taala ne tujh ko be-gunah aur paak farmaya'' meri maan ne kaha : uth aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tareef kar aur shukr kar aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sar ka bosa ley. maine kaha : Allah ki qism main to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf nahi uthungi aur na kisi ki tareef karungi siwaey Allah Taala ke usi ne meri paaki utari. Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Allah Taala ne ( إِنَّ الَّذِينَ جَاءُوا بِالْإِفْكِ عُصْبَةٌ مِّنكُمْ لَا تَحْسَبُوهُ شَرًّا لَّكُم بَلْ هُوَ خَيْرٌ لَّكُمْ ( ) ۲۴ - النور : ۱۱ ( aakhir tak das aayaton ko to Allah ne un aayaton ko meri paaki ke liye utara. saiyedna Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo Mistah (Raziallahu anhu) se azeez daari ki wjah se sulook kya kartey they ye kaha : ke Allah ki qism ! ab main usko kuchh na doonga kyonke usne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki nisbat aisa kaha to Allah ne ye aayat utari ( وَلاَ يَأْتَلِ أُولُو الْفَضْلِ مِنْكُمْ وَالسَّعَةِ أَنْ يُؤْتُوا أُولِى الْقُرْبَى ( se ( أَلاَ تُحِبُّونَ أَنْ يَغْفِرَ اللَّهُ لَكُمْ ( aakhir tak. Hibban bin-Musa ne kaha : Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ne kaha : ye aayat badi ummeed ki hai Allah ki kitab mein kyonke usmein Allah Taala ne naate-daaron ke sath achcha sulook karne mein bakhshish ka wada kya. saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! main ye chahta hun ke Allah mujh ko bakhshey, phir Mistah (Raziallahu anhu) ko jo kuchh diya kartey they wo jari kar diya aur kaha : main kabhi band na karunga. Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aur Rasulullah ne Ummul-Momenin Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) se mere baab mein puchha : jo wo janti hun ya unhon-ne dekha ho. unhon-ne kaha : (halanke wo saukan thin) ya Rasulullah ! main apne kaan aur aankh ki ehtiyat rakhti hun (yani bin suney koi baat suni hai nahi kehti aur na bin dekhey ko dekhi kehti hon) main to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko nek hi samajhti hun. Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Zenab (Raziallahu anha) hi aik bevi thin jo mere muqabil ki thin Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon main aur Allah Taala ne unko us tohmat se bachaya unki parhezgari ki wjah se aur unki behan Hamna binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ne unke liye tassub kya aur unke liye ladin to jo log tabah huey unmein wo bhi thin (yani tohmat mein Sharik thin) Zohri ne kaha : to un logon ka ye aakhir haal hai jo ham ko pahuncha."
7021,"abu Rabe Atki ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Fulaih bin Sulaiman ne hadis sunai, neez hamein Hasan-bin-Ali Hulwani aur abd bin Humaid ne hadis sunai, donon ne kaha : hamein Yaqoob-bin-Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) bin Sad ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne Saleh bin kaisaan se hadis sunai, un donon (Fulaih bin Sulaiman aur Saleh bin kaisaan) ne Zohri se Yunus aur Mamar ki riwayat ke mutabiq unhi ki sanad ke sath (yahi) hadis bayan ki. Fulaih ki hadis mein isi tarah hai jaisey Mamar ne bayan kya : unhein (qabaaili) hamiyat ne jahiliyat (ke daur) mein ghaseet liya aur Saleh ki hadis mein Yunus ke qaul ki tarah hai : unhein (qabaaili) hamiyat ne uksaa diya aur Saleh ki hadis mein mazeed ye hai : Urwa ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) is baat ko na-pasand karti thin ke Hassan (bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu)) ko unke samney bura-bhala kaha jaey. wo farmati thin : unhon-ne ye (azeem sher) kaha hai : be-shak mera bap aur iska bap aur meri izzat, tum logon se Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aabru ki hifazat ke liye dhaal hain. aur unhon-ne mazeed bhi kaha : Urwa ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : Allah ki qasam! jis shakhs ke barey mein wo saari baatein, jo ghadi gaee thin, wo kehta tha : Subhan-Allah! (ye kaisi baatein hain) us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai! maine kabhi kisi aurat ke hajla ursi (tak ka ( parda bhi nahi uthaya. (hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : phir baad mein wo Allah ki raah mein qatl ho kar Shahid ho gaya aur Yaqoob-bin-Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki hadis main (موعرين في نحر الظهيرة) ( log do-pahar ke waqt be saaya banjar rastey main safar se be haal ho gaey they.) Abdur-Razzaq ne ( موغرين ( (garmi ki shiddat se be haal huey) kaha hai. abd bin Humaid ne kaha : maine Abdur-Razzaq se puchha : ( موغرين (ka matlab kya hai? kaha : ( الوغرة ( garmi ki shiddat hoti hai."
7022,"abu-Usama ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se riwayat ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab mere mamley main wo baatein kahi gain jo kahi gain aur mujhey us mamley ka ilm na tha, (is waqt) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba dene ke liye khadey huey. shahaadatein padhein, Allah ki hamd w sana ki jo iske shaayaane-shaan hai, phir farmaya is (hamd w sana) ke baad ! mujhey un logon ke barey mein mashwara do jinhoney meri ahliya par bohtan lagaya aur main Allah ki qism khata hun ke meri ahliya ke khilaf kabhi koi burai mere ilm mein nahi aai. wo ( Safwan bin Muattal (Raziallahu anhu)) jiske barey mein unhon-ne tohmat lagai hai, Allah ki qism ! mujhey iske barey mein kisi burai ka ilm nahi, wo kabhi mere ghar nahi aaya magar us waqt jab main maujood tha aur main kabhi safar ki wjah se (Madina se) ghair hazir nahi raha magar wo bhi (is safar mein) mere sath (Madina se) ghair hazir tha aur poorey waqiey samet hadis bayan ki aur is mein ye ( bhi) hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere ghar mein dakhil huey aur meri khaadima se poochha. usne kaha : Allah ki qasam! main unmein koi aik aib bhi nahi janti, iske siwa ke wo so jaya karti thin aur bakri andar aati aur unka aata ya kaha : unka Khameer (jo aatey mein milaya jata hai) kha jati. Hisham ko shak hua hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik sathi ne jhidkiyaan din aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bilkul sach bataao, yahan tak ke us mamley mein un logon ne usey tehqeer aamez baatein kahin to usne jawab mein kaha : Subhan-Allah! Allah ki qasam! main unke barey mein bilkul isi tarah janti hun jis tarah sunaar khalis soney ko janta hai. (unmein zarra barabar khot nahi, wo khalis sona hain.) aur ye mamla us shakhs tak pahuncha jiske barey mein ye baat kahi gaee to usne kaha : Subhan-Allah! Allah ki qism ! maine aaj tak kisi aurat ki khilwat gaah ka parda bhi nahi uthaya. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : wo izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ki raah mein qatl ho kar Shahid ho gaya aur is hadis mein mazeed ye baat bhi hai ke jin logon ne (bohtan par mabni) baatein ki thin unmein mistah, hamna aur Hassan (bin Sabit ( (Raziallahu anhu) they. aur munafiq Abdullah-bin-Ubai wo shakhs tha jo ( seedhey saadhey waqiey ke andar se) jhootey ilzam nikaalta tha aur (bohtan ki jhooti kahaani ki sura mein) unhein yakjaa karta tha. usi ne us bohtan taraashi mein sabse bada kirdaar sanbhaala aur (iske baad) Hamna (Raziallahu anhu) thi."
7023,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik shakhs ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Umme- walad (aap ke farzand ki walida (ke sath muttahim kya jata tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : jao aur uski gardan uda do, Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) uske paas gaey to wo aik uthley (kam gahrey ( kuwein mein thandak ke liye ghusl kar raha tha, Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : niklo , aur) sahara dene ke liye) usey apna hath pakdaaya aur usey bahar nikala to dekha ke wo heejda hai, iska uzu (khaas ang) makhsus tha hi nahi. is par Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) (usko qatl karne se) ruk gaey aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! wo to heejdaa hai, iska uzu (khaas ang) makhsoos hai hi nahi."
